  "text": "scaffold, and enhanced cartilage repair of an osteochondral defect in a 6 week period. With the advancement of cellular reprogramming techniques, it is now possible to generate iPSCs using an integration-free approach, which is safer and more amenable from a regulatory perspective for their eventual clinical use. [CITATION_1] Despite this decreased risk of unwanted tissues, further studies are needed to better assess the longterm benefit of using human iPSCs for articular cartilage tissue engineering.",
